'''三星智付'''（{{lang-en|'''Samsung-{}- Pay'''}}）是[[韩国|韩国]][[三星电子|三星电子]]的一种基于[[近場通訊|近場通訊]]（NFC）技術与[[磁信号安全传输|磁信号安全传输]]（MST）技術的[[移动支付|移动支付]]、[[电子现金|电子现金]]以及會員卡管理服务<ref>{{cite|title=Samsung Smart Pay NFC + MST - YouTube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=55j3Ep6qM_0|date=2 March 2015|accessdate=2015-12-29|archive-date=2015-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151120044623/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=55j3Ep6qM_0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite|title=What is MST (Magnetic Secure Transmission)? - Samsung|url=http://www.samsung.com/us/support/answer/ANS00043865/997410383|accessdate=2015-12-29|archive-date=2015-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151229061734/http://www.samsung.com/us/support/answer/ANS00043865/997410383/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，让消费者可以在支持三星智付的[[三星Galaxy|三星Galaxy]]行動裝置上进行款项支付。三星智付不需使用特殊的非接觸型終端設備，可直接在支援NFC的读取器以及银行卡读取器上直接接触使用。<ref name="#1">{{cite|title=Samsung PAY - Youtube|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=285QYIUqhnQ|author=Next Level Tech|date=28 August 2015|accessdate=2015-12-29|archive-date=2016-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316182458/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=285QYIUqhnQ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=jason>{{cite|title=Here's why Samsung Pay is way better than Apple Pay and Android Pay|url=http://fortune.com/2015/09/30/samsung-pay-review/|author=Jason Cipriani|date=September 30, 2015|accessdate=2015-12-29|archive-date=2015-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151205153848/http://fortune.com/2015/09/30/samsung-pay-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

